- By applying logarithm and exponential properties, we have

  $$
  \begin{align*}
  M &= -2.5\big[\log(F)-\log(F_0)\big] \tag*{\textbf{M1}}\\[10pt]
  M &= -2.5\cdot\log(F)+2.5\cdot\log(F_0) \\[11pt]
  2.5\cdot\log(F) &= 2.5\cdot \log(F_0) - M \\[8pt]
  \log(F) &= \log(F_0)- \dfrac{M}{2.5} \\[7pt]
  F &= F_0 \cdot 10^{-\frac{M\rule[-1pt]{0pt}{6pt}}{2.5}} \tag*{\textbf{A1}}
  \end{align*}
  $$

- Using the previous answer, we have

  $$
  \begin{align*}
  \dfrac{F_1}{F_6} &= \dfrac{\cancel{F_0} \cdot 10^{-\frac{1\rule[-1pt]{0pt}{6pt}}{2.5}}}{\cancel{F_0}\cdot  10^{-\frac{6\rule[-1pt]{0pt}{6pt}}{2.5}}} \\[10pt]
  &= \dfrac{10^{-\frac{1\rule[-1pt]{0pt}{6pt}}{2.5}}}{10^{-\frac{6\rule[-1pt]{0pt}{6pt}}{2.5}}} \\[10pt]
  &= 10^{\frac{6\rule[-1pt]{0pt}{6pt}}{2.5}-\frac{1\rule[-1pt]{0pt}{6pt}}{2.5}}\\[10pt]
  &= 10^{2} \\[10pt]
  &\hspace{0.28em}\answer{= 100} \tag*{\textbf{A1}}
  \end{align*}
  $$

- Using logarithm properties again, we obtain

  $$
  \begin{align*}
  M_2-M_1 &= -2.5\log\left(\dfrac{F_2}{F_0}\right) - \left[-2.5\log\left(\dfrac{F_1}{F_0}\right)\right] \\[10pt]
  &= -2.5\left[\log\left(\dfrac{F_2}{F_0}\right)-\log\left(\dfrac{F_1}{F_0}\right)\right]\tag*{\textbf{M1}} \\[10pt]
  &= -2.5\left[\log\left(\dfrac{F_2}{F_0}\div\dfrac{F_1}{F_0}\right)\right] \\[10pt]
  &= -2.5\left[\log\left(\dfrac{F_2}{F_0}\div\dfrac{F_1}{F_0}\right)\right] \\[10pt]
  &\hspace{0.27em}\answer{= -2.5 \log\left(\dfrac{F_2}{F_1}\right)}\tag*{\textbf{A1}}
  \end{align*}
  $$

- From part (c), we have

  $$
  \begin{align*}
  -2.5 \log\left(\dfrac{F_s}{F_m}\right) &= M_s-M_m \\[10pt]
  \log\left(\dfrac{F_s}{F_m}\right) &= \dfrac{-26.8-(-12.7)}{-2.5} \tag*{\textbf{A1}}\\[10pt]
  \dfrac{F_s}{F_m} &=10^{\tfrac{-14.1}{-2.5}} \\[10pt]
  &\hspace{0.28em}\answer{a=14.1 \text{ and }b=2.5} \tag*{\textbf{A1}}
  \end{align*}
  $$
